2016-10-7  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Introduced ShadowMap class and implemented shadow mapping (first draft).
	* Lights now have their light space matrix.
	* Moved rendering from RenderPass to RenderTechnique, since every render pass will implement its own.
	* Added convenient functions to reduce shader code, for pre and post lighting and lighting computations.
	* Added a way to retrieve the textures count from creation flags, in Pipeline.
	* Moved the scene management from RenderPass to derived classes.
	* Splitted Camera and Viewport Update function, added an Apply function so Update doesn't need an active Context any more.
	* Added SIMD wrapper Float4.
	* Fixed File and TextFile.
	* Fixed a double lock problem in same thread in Logger.

