	* Updated GlslExpr.cpp to be able to compile it with gcc 4.9...
	* Removed HdrLoader class, since I use FreeImage to load HDR images.
	* HDR is implemented, created some tone mapping algorithms.

2016-03-17  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Few updates in context to make the cleanup more correct. Still some work to do though.

2016-03-16  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Added GpuQuery class into Castor3D.

2016-03-14  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Added ManagerView class, to make the scene clean its resources, and being able not to clean Engine up when reloading the scene.
	* Added manager views for Samplers, Materials, Meshes and RenderWindows in Scene.
	* Still some problems with Contexts, but the most important stuff is done.
	* HDR rendering is implemented.
	* Created a first draft of HdrLoader, since FreeImage clamps floating point values to [0,1], still need some work though.

2016-03-12  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* The HDR is not rendering yet, but all the code is here

2016-03-11  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Each technique plugin has been cleaned up from C3D_HAS_GL_RENDERER preprocessor conditions.
	* Shaders creation have been moved from GlRenderSystem to RenderSystem.
	* Pixel shader creation common to Msaa, Ssaa, and Direct technique plugins have been moved to Castor3D::Technique.

