2016-02-12  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Modified FileParser so it does not use variadic parameters anymore.
	* Updated FileParser, to make its error reporting more consistent.
	* Modified SceneFileParser_Parsers so it defaults to DirectRenderTechnique if the requested one does not exist.
	* Reviewed ParserParameters.
	* Added a new parser: start_animation, and an option to animation: looped.
	* Fixed the parsing of unexpected additional parameters, so they are given to the parser function, as text.
	* The animations are unlinked, it was related to the shader that switches from one geometry to another, causing the bones matrices to be given to the wrong shader.
	* Updated translations.

