	* An AStyle pass, and fixed the submodule.
	* An AStyle pass, and fixed the submodule.
	* Removed the ShaderProgram from GeometryBuffers::Draw and GeometryBuffers::DrawInstanced.
	* Removed some unused sections in SceneFileParser.
	* Removed the ShaderProgram from GeometryBuffers::Draw and GeometryBuffers::DrawInstanced.
	* Removed some unused sections in SceneFileParser.
	* Reenabled eELEMENT_USAGE, as flags, so we can try and guess possible usages for attributes, from the name.
	* The split of the bones data from the vertex buffer works correctly.
	* Need to test the instantiation.
	* Need to find a way to match ProgramInputLayout elements with BufferDeclaration ones. The name matching is done, but I need an additional way, since names may not match.
	* Still need to fix the linked animated objects bug.
	* It renders, nearly correctly (Bob the guard has some problems with its textures).
	* I still need to do something, to remove the ProgramInputLayout::SetStride method, but I don't know how.
	* Renamed ShaderProgramBase to ShaderProgram, and TextureBase to Texture.

