2016-01-30  Sylvain Doremus  <dragonjoker59@hotmail.com>
	* Few corrections in README.
	* Fixed the non animated scenes camera, in scene files.
	* Small fix in SceneNode, to avoid an unwanted warning when reparenting a node.
	* Fixed Python binding.
	* Compiled with GCC, fixed all the projects, except for the Python bindings.
	* Removed billboards, geometries, cameras, lights, scene nodes, and animated objects groups lists from Scene.
	* Created a manager for each of those.
	* Create intermediate classes ResourceManager and ObjectManager, owned respectively by Engine and Scene, in order to have a better distinction between Engine managers and Scene managers.
	* Removed all virtual methods from managers, there is no polymorphism there so no need for them.
	* Reworked constructors of managed classes to be able to create them through basic Create method in the managers.
	* Also modified OwnedBy< Engine > and OwnedBy< RenderSystem > so their method to get the owner is named respectively GetEngine and GetRenderSystem.
	* Added an OwnedBy< Scene > in the same way.

